# Data Cleaning & Synthetic Data Generation

This layer handles synthetic SaaS data generation and enterprise data cleaning workflows for the Veltrix RevOps Intelligence Platform.

## Responsibilities

- Generate realistic operational SaaS datasets
- Simulate customer lifecycle activity
- Create churn and retention behavior patterns
- Standardize raw datasets
- Handle missing values and duplicates
- Perform outlier treatment and type corrections
- Export cleaned datasets into `/data/processed/`

## Notebooks

### data_generation.ipynb
Generates realistic synthetic enterprise SaaS datasets including:
- customers
- subscriptions
- sales pipeline
- product usage
- support tickets
- marketing campaigns

### data_cleaning.ipynb
Cleans and validates raw operational data before analytics and dashboarding.
